I'm just an AI, I don't have personal plans or schedules, but I can certainly help you plan out your week!

It sounds like you've got a great start to the week with your volleyball game today, and I'm sure you'll have a blast with your teammates afterwards.

What about the rest of the week? Do you have any other fitness activities or games scheduled? Are you planning on hitting the gym, going for a run, or trying out a new workout class?

Let me know, and I can offer some suggestions or tips to help you stay motivated and crush your fitness goals!
